{"tid":35124,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣失去熱誠既興趣","createTime":"2016-12-12T01:14:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T04:54:13.000Z","uid":51575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c3d448d2396718553c4afc718dd3eec7a13e21ec","tid":35124,"uid":51575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:14:53.000Z","msg":"高中開始鍾意行山影風景相<br />\n啲相影到出黎俾人讚好開心<br />\n無奈自己只有傻瓜機冇令機<br />\n所以攝影技術停滯不前<br />\n加上而家已經投身社會<br />\n冇左好多時間上山影相<br />\n對攝影已經開始失去熱誠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當年個個仲叫我做追日少年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828c46460df125b73fbe697471d4d8ea628db8a9","tid":35124,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:21:54.000Z","msg":"結他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fd27ee9ad92eebd3ba2b883c1dfa185dec857ad","tid":35124,"uid":62218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:22:19.000Z","msg":"打籃球"},{"pid":"edb199b0732f811c26346ead133898ef6d90229e","tid":35124,"uid":51575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打籃球</blockquote><br />\n打籃球我仲可以收工夜晚落去打<br />\n不過就好難約齊班波友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2585e188f02b38d4cf0fc161090961a9f41911f3","tid":35124,"uid":1517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:24:13.000Z","msg":"好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左個頭好快又冇興趣，樣樣識少少"},{"pid":"708351816fe91078b88feac5e7d2f263b2ec2978","tid":35124,"uid":51575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-12T01:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開左個頭好快又冇興趣，樣樣識少少</blockquote><br />\n有冇啲堅持左一段時間然後先冇興趣既興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eddd91ce7d02708aea5d14a807399ff38bed36","tid":35124,"